devdoc.details: This library follows the algorithms described in [VRF-draft-06](https://datatracker.ietf.org/doc/html/draft-irtf-cfrg-vrf-06) and [RFC6979](https://tools.ietf.org/html/rfc6979). It supports the _SECP256R1_SHA256_TAI_ cipher suite, i.e. the aforementioned algorithms using `SHA256` and the `Secp256R1` curve.
